;; REAL DATA — world national LEGISLATURES (the legislative-branch layer worldwide).
;; Per founder directive to raise coverage to 全世界政府. One-time maintainer pull of
;; the Wikidata SPARQL endpoint 2026-06-03: each CURRENT UN member's legislative body
;; (wdt:P194), the body not dissolved (no P576), + official site (P856). Exact QIDs
;; parsed from the SPARQL JSON (no summarizing model). Bicameral systems whose country
;; lists more than one P194 keep the first (the parliament-as-whole / primary chamber).
;;
;; :level :legislature (new level, see gov-atlas-ontology :gov.unit/level doc),
;; :branch :legislative, parent = the country unit gov.<iso>. Every row :authoritative
;; + :maintainer-verified. :official-url / :provenance = the legislature's OWN site
;; (P856) else the Wikidata entity. Observational mirror (G3/G11): descriptive,
;; neutral, never an official channel, never ranked. Live ingest + publication remain
;; operator/Council steps.

